panels.name: 400s Last 7 Days
panels.queryString:
$$haProxy
| parse "]: *:* [*] * * */*/*/*/* * * * * * */*/*/*/* */* " as client_ip,client_port,date_time_main,frontend_name_transport,backend_name,Tq,Tw,Tc,Tr,Tt,status_code,bytes_read,captured_request_cookie,captured_response_cookie,termination_state_with_cookie_status,actconn,feconn,beconn,srv_conn,retries,srv_queue,backend_queue nodrop
| parse regex "\s\"(?<http_request>[GET|HEAD|POST|PUT|DELETE|CONNECT|OPTIONS|TRACE|PATCH].*)\"" nodrop
| parse field=http_request "* * *" as http_method,url,http_protocol nodrop
| where status_code matches "4*"
| timeslice 15m
| count as _400s by _timeslice 
| compare with timeshift 1d 7

panels.name: Top 400s and 500s by Request

| parse "]: *:* [*] * * */*/*/*/* * * * * * */*/*/*/* */* " as client_ip,client_port,date_time_main,frontend_name_transport,backend_name,Tq,Tw,Tc,Tr,Tt,status_code,bytes_read,captured_request_cookie,captured_response_cookie,termination_state_with_cookie_status,actconn,feconn,beconn,srv_conn,retries,srv_queue,backend_queue nodrop

| parse field=http_request "* * *" as http_method,url,http_protocol nodrop
| where status_code matches "5*" or status_code matches "4*"
| count as count by status_code, http_request
| fields status_code, count, http_request
| sort count
